    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现在是时候了解荒地的危险了。你一生都在为成为队长之一而训练。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >长老会已经给了你第一个严肃的任务。你必须带领你的人民穿越荒地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是第一次，你获得了第三级技术。这让你可以使用车辆，让你可以探索更多的地形。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要准备必要的设备和资源。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >荒地在等着你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130380/extras/66f405763f1dbe826a76984a0352435a.poster.avif?t=1728241360\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130380/extras/66f405763f1dbe826a76984a0352435a.webm?t=1728241360\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130380/extras/66f405763f1dbe826a76984a0352435a.mp4?t=1728241360\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>在堕落世界的灰烬上恢复文明! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130380/extras/1793e612167d254011e59e7f7bbf2da5.poster.avif?t=1728241360\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130380/extras/1793e612167d254011e59e7f7bbf2da5.webm?t=1728241360\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130380/extras/1793e612167d254011e59e7f7bbf2da5.mp4?t=1728241360\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>拾荒和收集资源，一切都算数! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130380/extras/391eeb9aa0a181c3bae165eebe1d950c.poster.avif?t=1728241360\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130380/extras/391eeb9aa0a181c3bae165eebe1d950c.webm?t=1728241360\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130380/extras/391eeb9aa0a181c3bae165eebe1d950c.mp4?t=1728241360\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>在世界末日之后，建设和管理幸存者的城市。照顾好生活的方方面面。采集、建设、耕种、升级、胜利! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130380/extras/069d817db75bd3a1174258b1637094c3.poster.avif?t=1728241360\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130380/extras/069d817db75bd3a1174258b1637094c3.webm?t=1728241360\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130380/extras/069d817db75bd3a1174258b1637094c3.mp4?t=1728241360\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>探索荒地，收集资源，保护和照顾你的人民!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130380/extras/20c18eb0df9d72a500c651eb86b1de0e.poster.avif?t=1728241360\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130380/extras/20c18eb0df9d72a500c651eb86b1de0e.webm?t=1728241360\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2130380/extras/20c18eb0df9d72a500c651eb86b1de0e.mp4?t=1728241360\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>探索荒地，收集资源，保护和照顾你的人民</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击退突袭者、野生部落民和自然灾害。</p>",
